{"tid":1745622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法官判蒙面法暫緩到本月29日！！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:50:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":18,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0f983885228d666cd7a63ccbe0ba76f5b1b083","tid":1745622,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:12:28.000Z","msg":"高等法院早前裁定緊急法於「危害公安」時可立法這部份違憲，而蒙面法主要條文亦違憲。律政司一方及後表明會提上訴，並申請暫緩判決，要求法庭頒佈暫時有效令，以待上訴法庭作進一步裁決。法官林雲浩及周家明昨日聽罷雙方陳詞，宣告蒙面法、緊急法涉案條文違憲，並拒絕律政司申請，但基於律政司將上訴，故暫緩裁決至本月29日或另作命令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60297111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60297111&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=fe998b2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191122%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60297111&h=848c160d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191122&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60297111</a>"},{"pid":"bf4644517d1779b27a728ee7c8d2b3671f1983de","tid":1745622,"uid":19176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7b3bb1c4b2953c2d979c235039f813f0e3fe7e","tid":1745622,"uid":213978,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"人權法過左 識驚了？"},{"pid":"5e35c70ff75d2fd17f5e004ec7726e33af181407","tid":1745622,"uid":286412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣